I fear with Title 42, if they do repeal it, I think things are fixing to get even worse,? referring to the administrations plan to lift COVID restrictions for illegal immigrants crossing into the U.S.
Biden should be given an honorary membership in the Mexican drug cartels because nobody has done more to help the cartels than Biden with his open border policies,? DeSantis said.
